1
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,280
Hurry up. Go, go.

2
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:11,000
Young Madam, you're amazing.

3
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:13,039
Adai, go play by yourself for a while.

4
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,300
I need to talk to Chuyi.

5
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:14,880
Go on.

6
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,960
Chuyi, don't mind what they said.

7
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:25,760
Sister-in-law, did I cause trouble for the Marquis Manor?

8
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:28,480
We're family. You're never a burden.

9
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,640
Chuyi.

10
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:33,000
Don't you want to tell us about the academy?

11
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,400
There's nothing to say.

12
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,600
Those who bully you

13
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:42,479
won't stop just because you suffer in silence.

14
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:45,360
Did I really do something wrong?

15
00:01:45,800 --> 00:01:47,120
Gossip is a fearful thing.

16
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:49,120
Sometimes malice strikes on a whim.

17
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:51,120
But whenever I see them,

18
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:53,280
I think it's my own fault.

19
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,520
It's not your fault.

20
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,000
They are the cowards.

21
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,200
Like a mindless mob,

22
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,480
hurting others for their own amusement.

23
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:05,440
Brother told me to be brave and face it.

24
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,800
But I'm still scared of them.

25
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,160
Actually, everyone

26
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,040
gets scared.

27
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:16,360
But true courage is that when you are scared,

28
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,090
you still choose to face it.

29
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:21,420
Why am I not a biological daughter of the Bai family?

30
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,000
You are Bai Chuyi.

31
00:02:23,160 --> 00:02:24,760
A child of the Marquis Manor.

32
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:26,220
No matter what others say,

33
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,160
your worth

34
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,720
won't be diminished by their words.

35
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:34,160
Sister-in-law, teach me martial arts from now on.

36
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,620
I want to become stronger.

37
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:36,280
Okay.

38
00:02:39,040 --> 00:02:39,900
It's a promise.

39
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,560
To have such a virtuous wife,

40
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:46,200
is a great blessing for the Bai family.

41
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:50,920
Why isn't Huanghuacai this gentle with me?

42
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:54,530
You have thick skin. Be glad she doesn't beat you.

43
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,840
My good wife.

44
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,100
What are you doing?

45
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:08,200
I realized I haven't given you a gift since we got married.

46
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:11,520
So I plan to paint a picture for you.

47
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,160
You know how to paint?

48
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,840
The Madam keeps a tight leash on me,

49
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:19,760
so how would she know I have such talent?

50
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,840
Sit still. Don't move.

51
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:29,760
Wait.

52
00:04:19,880 --> 00:04:21,399
This is the painting you made?

53
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,720
How is it? Do you like it?

54
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,040
I heard my mother say,

55
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,920
the daylily is also known as the 'sorrow-forgetting grass'.

56
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,280
It grows in the mountains,

57
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,640
peaceful and uncontentious.

58
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:32,920
It can convey longing

59
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,720
and dissolve sorrow.

60
00:04:35,159 --> 00:04:38,680
In my heart, you are like this daylily.

61
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,880
Having weathered wind and rain,

62
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:43,050
you remain resilient, facing the sun.

63
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:44,600
Such fine weather

64
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:47,040
makes me want to compose a poem.

65
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:50,960
Your poetry leaves much to be desired.

66
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:55,800
Looking down on me? Listen.

67
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:06,360
Daylilies sway under the clear sky,

68
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:11,960
A gentle breeze brushes through the fragrant clumps.

69
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:15,360
Vying not for spring, as years go by,

70
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:19,880
Drifting across the river, forgetting sorrow.

71
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:24,760
Drifting across the river, forgetting sorrow.

72
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,820
Young Madam, the Marquis asks you to go over.

73
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,650
The Marquis is looking for you.

74
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,260
Greetings, Third Prince.

75
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,520
Miss Song.

76
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,240
Why does everyone like calling her Miss Song?

77
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,600
And not Lady Bai?

78
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,280
Brother, what are you saying?

79
00:06:08,280 --> 00:06:09,040
Nothing.

80
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,080
Move over.

81
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,860
You're blocking my view of the Third Prince.

82
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,280
Go, go, go.

83
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:17,960
Your Highness,

84
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,080
what brings you here?

85
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,920
Regarding the poisoning of my father,

86
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:24,720
I suspect Prince Bulei and Princess Tuoya of the Grasslands are involved.

87
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:27,000
Do you have any evidence, Your Highness?

88
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,840
Bulei feigns submission,

89
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:31,240
but his movements are secretive.

90
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,840
And Princess Tuoya,

91
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,960
is well-versed in grassland witchcraft.

92
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:37,520
I have no choice but to suspect them.

93
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,240
Without evidence,

94
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,640
making rash accusations

95
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,720
will only complicate matters.

96
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,480
So we just do nothing?

97
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:48,000
The best course of action now isn't a direct confrontation,

98
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,360
but to protect yourself.

99
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,760
What do you mean?

100
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:54,600
If Bulei and Tuoya are indeed plotting something,

101
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,560
the Palace is the most dangerous place right now.

102
00:06:58,400 --> 00:06:59,600
Then what should I do?

103
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:02,160
Why don't you stay here at the Marquis of Zhongyi's Manor?

104
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,600
I'll send Afu to investigate the Palace.

105
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,440
Rest assured, Your Highness.

106
00:07:08,440 --> 00:07:10,440
With my daughter-in-law and me here,

107
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:12,720
no one will harm you.

108
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,560
In that case,

109
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,440
I'll impose on you both then.

110
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:21,850
Miss Song, I haven't seen you in years.

111
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:24,220
You've become even more impressive.

112
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,770
Please, just call me Song Xuan.

113
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,840
Back in the Palace,

114
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,640
if you hadn't intervened

115
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,080
and exposed the Noble Consort as a foreign spy

116
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,400
poisoning the princes,

117
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:37,640
I might have died like the others.

118
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:41,020
You were blessed by fortune, Your Highness.

119
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,360
I once thought...

120
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,920
about marrying you.

121
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,370
I thought back then,

122
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,200
you were skilled in martial arts

123
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,460
and incredibly brave.

124
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:56,200
If you became my princess,

125
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,880
perhaps

126
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:01,080
we could have guarded the borders together.

127
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:02,210
Calm down, Brother.

128
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:06,700
So the Third Prince wanted to marry Sister-in-law.

129
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,880
Thanks, Brother.

130
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,410
What do you mean?

131
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:12,440
Nothing.

132
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,970
Just glad you married her quickly.

133
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:18,400
Otherwise, I definitely couldn't compete with Sister-in-law.

134
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:19,680
Such a rough woman.

135
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,050
I wouldn't like her.

136
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,120
I think Sister-in-law is great.

137
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,600
She's valiant,

138
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,040
and very smart.

139
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,320
I think so too.

140
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,920
You are a lucky man, Brother Bai.

141
00:08:31,200 --> 00:08:31,640
Yes.

142
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,240
Actually, I...

143
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:41,600
The weather is really nice today.

144
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,559
Oh,

145
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,760
Your Highness,

146
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,210
you're here too.

147
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:49,280
What were you chatting about with my wife?

148
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,440
Nothing much.

149
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:53,320
Just reminiscing about the past.

150
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,280
The past isn't important.

151
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,640
The present is what matters.

152
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,400
If back then...

153
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,260
Your Highness.

154
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:05,850
Brother Bai,

155
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,400
I really envy you.

156
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:10,200
Sometimes I envy myself too.

157
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,200
You two carry on.

158
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,690
I won't disturb you.

159
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:27,720
I have good news for you, Miss Shen.

160
00:09:28,160 --> 00:09:31,960
Song Xuan has been investigating the missing 500,000 in military funds.

161
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,560
What does that have to do with me?

162
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:35,200
The Bai Manor can handle it.

163
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,960
You have impressive methods, Miss Shen.

164
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,080
There's more.

165
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:42,770
I wonder what you think, Miss Shen,

166
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,010
about the Dasheng Emperor's illness?

167
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,170
Princess Toya is still testing me.

168
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:51,020
Why do you say that, Miss Shen?

169
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:54,330
I'm just curious about the fate of your Dasheng Emperor.

170
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,880
He can die.

171
00:09:56,640 --> 00:09:58,000
But not right now.

172
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,520
Marquis Bai hasn't shown his hand yet.

173
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,920
Not to mention Song Xuan.

174
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,400
You have no chance of winning.

175
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,880
So what do you mean?

176
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:11,800
The Emperor just needs to have one breath left.

177
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:14,600
That's enough for me to stage a good show.

178
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,280
What do you plan to do, Miss Shen?
